.DT
start_combat
Disk World creator help
start_combat

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
start_combat -  This method is called when combat starts.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void start_combat(object opponent)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^opponent%^RESET%^ - The first opponent to be attacked.

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/living/combat.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method is called when combat starts.  You can overload this function
to make your NPC do things at the start of combat.
You do not need to call ::start_combat() since this is just a stub function.

.EP

